# Agent Bootstrap

- Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) before product-shaping or implementation work.
- Read [SECURITY.md](../../SECURITY.md) and [docs/data_handling_policy.md](../../docs/data_handling_policy.md) before changes that touch data handling, auth, Docker, CI, or dependencies.
- Do not commit raw financial data, credentials, or local runtime artifacts.
- Use branches and pull requests; do not push directly to `main`.
- Include a human QA script in PR notes for app, UI, API, or Docker behavior changes.
- For owner product/architecture/privacy decisions, use [.cursor/skills/decision-card-review/SKILL.md](../../.cursor/skills/decision-card-review/SKILL.md) and persist approved outcomes in planning docs.
